{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because the guy filled up big cans and-- and handed them to other German soldiers that carried them away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then he was done with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had our-- our-- our eating dishes with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was always with us, hanging us, on the string-- on the stringy belt that we had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we would hang-- hold our dish over towards this thing, that this soldier could easily have filled up-- filled up one of those big carafes, or what he had, and poured it in to us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he we all held it out to have some of this hot stuff, which was probably coffee, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He-- he looked-- at-- at one time he looked at us straight, opened the spigot of that big kettle, and let it run out right in front of us, onto the tracks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there for probably 10 days, two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The commander of that camp-- his-- his camp was overcrowded already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because all other areas of-- of outlying camps, the-- the Germans-- the Nazis-- put us into-- into Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so these guys wanted to get rid of us as soon as possible, obviously.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were then taken to another camp, the Heinkelwerke, which was a factory, an airplane factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there too, for a few days only.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we were loaded up again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were taken to a camp called Flossenburg, which is located in northern-- Northeast Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Flossenburg was a camp designed to hold 5,000 prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we arrived there, there were about 140,000 there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that time, though, we were not assigned to any working place anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We would be kept busy in head counts, from morning to evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Prisoners just dropped on the spot.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
